Katryn Anderson proposed following entry to
/usr/share/apps/kdm/sessions if you're using the
KDM login manager:
----------------------------------------------------------
[Desktop Entry]
Encoding=UTF-8 
Type=XSession
Exec=ncwm
TryExec=ncwm
Name=NCWM
Name[xx]=xxNCWMxx
Comment=No Cheese Window Manager
Comment[xx]=xxNo Cheese Window Managerxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
----------------------------------------------------------
